{
        "name": "RandomForest-Classification",
        "description": "Helix Edge RandomForest-Classification based Classification Algorithm",
        "type": "Classification",
        "enabled": true,
        "outputFeaturesPredefined": true,
        "allowDeploymentAtEdge": true,
        "requiresDataPipeline": true,
        "predictionName": "classification",
        "isPredictionRealTime": true,
        "defaultPredictionEndpointUrl": "/api/v3/predict",
        "defaultPredictionPort": 48920,
        "trainerImagePath": "lpade:hedge-ml-trg-classification-randomforest",
        "trainerImageDigest": "sha256:42293382e31b91b2f1d4a6ff6e88057ec9a96e4310f7a4b9702c2a1e7fa7d318",
        "predictionImagePath": "hedge-ml-pred-classification-randomforest:25.1.00_latest",
        "predictionImageDigest": "sha256:47afdd31f991d2a42e3288a67924b709316bd7b1e22e7b7440e5848e34ff0fda",
        "predictionPayloadTemplate": {
            "name": "Classification",
            "payloadSample": "{\n\t\"correlation-id-01\" : [3, 3.14, 5],\n\t\"correlation-id-02\" : [5, 2.71, 3]\n}",
            "template": "{\n\t{{- $length := len .CollectedData -}}\n\t{{- $counter := 0 -}}\n\t{{- range $correlationID, $inferenceData := .CollectedData }}\n\t\"{{ $correlationID }}\" : [\n\t\t{{- range $i, $value := index $inferenceData.Data 0 -}}\n\t\t{{ if $i }}, {{ end }}{{- if eq (printf \"%T\" $value) \"string\" -}}\"{{ $value }}\"{{- else -}}{{ $value }}{{- end -}}\n\t\t{{- end -}}\n\t]{{ if lt (add $counter 1) $length }},{{ end }}\n\t{{- $counter = (add $counter 1) -}}\n\t{{- end -}}\n\t}"
        },
        "predictionOutputKeys": [
            "prediction"
        ],
        "autoEventGenerationRequired": true,
        "publishPredictionsRequired": true,
        "hyperParameters": {},
        "isOotb": true
    }
